      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>307 - Hours, Etc. (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">February 1999</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td width="45%"><strong>First Indicator</strong><br><em>Display constant controller</em><br># - Hours <br>8 - No display constant generated <br><br></td>
